The codefix for IDE0044 'Make field readonly' removes whitespace.

Pre-codefix:
```
namespace IDE0044_CodeFix_Removes_Whitespace
{
    public class C
    {
        int x;

int y;

public C(int x, int y)
        {
            this.x = x;
            this.y = y;
        }
    }
}
```

Post-codefix:
```
namespace IDE0044_CodeFix_Removes_Whitespace
{
    public class C
    {
        readonly int x;
        readonly int y;

public C(int x, int y)
        {
            this.x = x;
            this.y = y;
        }
    }
}
```

Shouldn't it respect my whitespace and change the code to this?
```
namespace IDE0044_CodeFix_Removes_Whitespace
{
    public class C
    {
        readonly int x;

readonly int y;

public C(int x, int y)
        {
            this.x = x;
            this.y = y;
        }
    }
}
```

